  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>1.17.12 is a minor update including some small features and bug fixes.</p><p>11:30 CT on September 16, 2020</p><h3 id=\"id-1.17.12-Enhancements\">Enhancements</h3><ul><li><p>The Payment Device screens for connection tests are now available to additional roles.</p></li><li><p>Ticket timers have been optimized for faster load times.</p></li><li><p>Uniqueness checks for records that have unique constraints (e.g. no two catalog items allowed with the same name) have been optimized for faster saves.</p></li><li><p>The notification queue now has a location filter, and is visible to location admins.</p></li></ul>",
